lead_paragraph: Kelsey Mitchell scored 22 points and No. 7 Ohio State used a big third quarter to take command and beat Rutgers 67-58 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Mitchell Scores 22, No. 7 Ohio State Beats Rutgers
